      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-ink-500">Model-agnostic by design: Apertus, Llama or Mistral — whichever wins on your evaluation set. The evaluation decides, not the logo.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-5 md:col-start-8">
      {% include "partials/diagram.njk" %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Compliance -->
